People act like we're crack dealers.

142
00:07:21,066 --> 00:07:22,817
沒人拿著槍去指向某人說
Nobody put a gun to anybody's head and said,

143
00:07:22,901 --> 00:07:26,320
"嘿 獵人 買下這棟你償還不起的房子吧 等你住進去以後
"Hey, nimrod, buy a house you can't afford. And you know what? While you're at it,

144
00:07:26,404 --> 00:07:28,447
再用它申請信用額度 這件就可以再買一艘船了"
put a line of credit on that baby and buy yourself a boat."

145
00:07:28,698 --> 00:07:30,950
巴菲特給你回復了嗎?
You heard anything from Buffett?

146
00:07:31,243 --> 00:07:35,496
他要求獲得股價為40美金的優先股 分紅為9%
He's asking for preferred shares at 40 with a dividend of 9%.

147
00:07:35,580 --> 00:07:37,998
股價剛還在66塊呢 搞什麼鬼啊?
We were just at 66. What the fuck?

148
00:07:38,083 --> 00:07:40,042
或許這只是遊戲的序幕吧 Dick
Maybe it's just an opening gambit, Dick.

149
00:07:40,168 --> 00:07:41,710
聽上去更像是一種侮辱
Sounds more like a goddamn insult.

150
00:07:41,795 --> 00:07:43,212
- 我來幫你弄吧 Dick  - 謝謝
- Let me get that, Dick.  - Thank you.

151
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:45,339
我們的股價已經跌到了36塊
We're at 36 right now.

152
00:07:45,882 --> 00:07:48,759
這幾個月以來我們從未到過66快附近
We haven't been anywhere near 66 in months.

153
00:07:48,844 --> 00:07:50,761
市場喜歡巴菲特
The markets like Buffett.

154
00:07:50,846 --> 00:07:53,639
- 他的名字會在一夜之間推動股價上升  - 我才不在乎他是誰
- His name will push the price up overnight.  - I don't care who he is,

155
00:07:53,807 --> 00:07:58,811
我不會用1年花費3億6000萬的代價去取悅他以謀求合作
I am not spending $360 million a year for the pleasure of doing business with him.

156
00:07:58,895 --> 00:08:00,020
房地產市場會重新振作起來的
Real estate will come back.

157
00:08:00,105 --> 00:08:01,647
韓國人有意介入
Koreans have been sniffing around.

158
00:08:01,731 --> 00:08:03,524
這不好了 他們不會漫天要價
There you go. And they won't steal us blind.

159
00:08:03,608 --> 00:08:06,360
這種場面以前我也經歷過 首席執行官們開始恐慌 然後廉價賣掉自己的股票
I've seen this before. CEOs panic and they sell out cheap.

160
00:08:06,444 --> 00:08:09,446
現在 整條華爾街都認為已經到了火燒眉毛的時候
Right now, the Street's running around with its hair on fire,

161
00:08:09,531 --> 00:08:11,407
但暴風雨總會過去的
but the storm always passes.

162
00:08:11,491 --> 00:08:16,120
我們要充滿信心 然後 去參加高盛舉辦的午宴
We stand strong, and on the other side, we'll eat Goldman's lunch.

163
00:08:18,165 --> 00:08:19,915
那我們該如何回復巴菲特呢?
So, what do we do about Buffett?

164
00:08:20,667 --> 00:08:23,627
去他媽的巴菲特
Screw Warren Buffett.

165
00:08:25,797 --> 00:08:27,423
每周早餐會議

166
00:08:25,797 --> 00:08:27,423
- 他拒絕了?  - 雷曼兄弟的股價
- He passed?  - Lehman dropped

167
00:08:27,507 --> 00:08:29,758
在今天上午已經跌到了28塊半 他到底是怎麼想的啊?
to 28 and a half this morning. What in the world is he thinking?

168
00:08:29,843 --> 00:08:33,846
他根本沒有思考 他是在妄想 他認為巴菲特的開價太高了
He's not thinking. He's delusional. He thought the ask was too high.

169
00:08:34,243 --> 00:08:38,601
Ben Bernanke 聯邦儲蓄主席

170
00:08:35,265 --> 00:08:36,682
他得去籌措資金啊
He's gotta raise cash.

171
00:08:36,766 --> 00:08:38,601
我也是這麼跟他說的
I told him that.

172
00:08:39,936 --> 00:08:42,104
- 我找格林斯潘談過了  - 真的嗎?
- I spoke to Greenspan.  - Really?

173
00:08:42,314 --> 00:08:47,568
他說住房市場供過於求 這就是問題所在
He says there's too much housing supply. That's the problem.

174
00:08:48,862 --> 00:08:53,449
所以我們應該買下所有閒置房屋 不讓它們流入市場
So we should buy up all the vacant houses and burn them.

175
00:09:00,665 --> 00:09:03,959
Dick需要一個能認清現狀的買家
Dick needs a buyer, someone with a grip on reality.

176
00:09:04,127 --> 00:09:06,295
幾個月前巴克萊銀行曾表示過些許興趣
Barclays expressed some interest a couple of months ago,

177
00:09:06,379 --> 00:09:08,130
但我覺得現在的股價還沒有降到他們的心理價位
but I don't think the price is low enough for them.

178
00:09:09,007 --> 00:09:11,217
- 美國銀行呢?  - 有這個可能
- Bank of America?  - Possible.

179
00:09:11,301 --> 00:09:13,177
Dick之前也試探過他們
Dick's put out feelers there before.

180
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:15,846
不過我們得保持低調
We have to keep it quiet, though.

181
00:09:15,931 --> 00:09:17,932
因為一旦有人獲悉他們準備出售
'Cause if anyone hears that they're trying to sell

182
00:09:18,141 --> 00:09:20,976
雷曼兄弟將瞬間完蛋
Lehman'll be dead within the hour.

183
00:09:21,311 --> 00:09:26,398
2008年6月11日 雷曼兄弟高管緊急決策會議

184
00:09:21,311 --> 00:09:23,479
在房地產業務上的投資正在毀掉整個公司
The real estate investments are killing the firm.

185
00:09:24,147 --> 00:09:26,398
我們得公開承認我們犯了一些錯誤
We have to admit publically we've made some mistakes.

186
00:09:26,566 --> 00:09:28,525
我們需要對高管層進行更替
We need to make a senior management change,

187
00:09:28,610 --> 00:09:30,694
從而向市場表明我們的立場
signal to the market that we get it.

188
00:09:32,239 --> 00:09:35,407
- 你們指的是誰?  - Joe Gregory
- Meaning what?  - Meaning Joe Gregory.

189
00:09:35,992 --> 00:09:38,452
別扯淡了
Get the fuck out of here.

190
00:09:40,038 --> 00:09:41,830
還輪不到你們來告訴我該如何來運營我的公司
You are not gonna tell me how to run my company.

191
00:09:41,957 --> 00:09:44,917
Joe在這場危機中沒有站在你這邊 這是人所共知的
Joe hasn't had your back on risk, and everyone knows it.

192
00:09:45,001 --> 00:09:48,337
Erin Callan也得走人 整條華爾街都知道她就是個笑話
Erin Callan's gotta go, too. As far as the Street's concerned, she's a joke.

193
00:09:48,463 --> 00:09:52,341
Joe Gregory和我共事了30多年
Joe Gregory has been with me for 30 years.

194
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:57,012
我們只是遇到了暫時性的困難 你們就想讓我把他攆走?
And you want me to kick him to the curb because we had a bad quarter?

195
00:09:57,097 --> 00:09:58,639
這不是暫時性的困難
It's not just a bad quarter.

196
00:09:58,723 --> 00:10:00,683
股價已經跌到23塊了
Stock hit 23.

197
00:10:00,767 --> 00:10:07,311
Skip McGee 雷曼兄弟投行部 全球區總裁

198
00:10:00,767 --> 00:10:04,311
23塊啊 公司大部分員工分到的股票都是在數年內無法進行買賣的
Twenty-three. Most of our guys are paid in stock they can't sell for years.

199
00:10:04,396 --> 00:10:07,022
他們損失的是過去六個月媮的淨利潤
They've lost most of their net worth over the last six months.

200
00:10:07,524 --> 00:10:11,068
如果你不穩住股價 你的那些交易員們只能跑路了
You don't stabilize the price, your traders are gonna jump ship.

201
00:10:11,236 --> 00:10:13,028
一群自私鬼
Selfish fucks.

202
00:10:13,113 --> 00:10:16,991
Dick 不僅是銀行家和交易員們 連客戶都會抽走他們的資金
It's not just bankers and traders, Dick. Clients are pulling their money.

203
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:19,785
公司將遭遇到連鎖反應
There's gonna be a run on this bank.

204
00:10:23,540 --> 00:10:25,541
消息靈通人士對財經頻道透露
Sources tell CNBC that both

205
00:10:25,625 --> 00:10:29,253
雷曼兄弟的Erin Callan和Joseph Gregory已經離任
Erin Callan and Joseph Gregory are out at Lehman Brothers.

206
00:10:29,379 --> 00:10:31,755
公司的主席Dick Fuld在一份聲明中稱
In a statement, the company's chairman, Dick Fuld, said

207
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,858
2008年8月4日

208
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:34,758
將由48歲的Bart McDade代替Gregory的位子
replacing Gregory with 48-year-old Bart McDade

209
00:10:34,758 --> 00:10:38,095
Bart McDade 雷曼兄弟新總裁兼首席運營官

210
00:10:34,843 --> 00:10:38,095
這是他所做過的最艱難的一個決定
has been one of the most difficult decisions he's had to make.

211
00:10:39,806 --> 00:10:42,558
Dick 韓國人剛剛到達Sullivan
Dick, the Koreans just arrived at Sullivan.

212
00:10:43,685 --> 00:10:44,852
我們一定要抓住這次機會
Let's go make this happen.

213
00:10:45,395 --> 00:10:47,730
我覺得這會兒你最好就待在這
My take is you'd be better off staying here for now.

214
00:10:49,566 --> 00:10:51,358
我們要把你打造成為"幕後人士"
We need you to be our "missing man."

215
00:10:51,901 --> 00:10:54,320
由我們去談 盡最大努力去促成這筆交易
We'll go in and push the deal as far as we can,

216
00:10:54,404 --> 00:10:57,990
最後再由你出面來達成這筆交易
and then we'll bring you in at the end to top it off.

217
00:10:58,158 --> 00:10:59,408
好吧 聽你的
All right, fine.

218
00:11:00,535 --> 00:11:02,328
很好
Okay. Okay.

219
00:11:07,917 --> 00:11:10,544
我們如期來到了紐約
We are committed to our presence in New York.

220
00:11:12,881 --> 00:11:15,924
但我們需要知道確切的數字
But we need to know that the underlying numbers make sense.

221
00:11:19,262 --> 00:11:21,930
我們也看到了事情的發展情況
We realize how things look.

222
00:11:22,015 --> 00:11:24,224
但我們的股價只是被一些做空者暫時挫傷
But our stock is getting hammered by the shorts.

223
00:11:24,642 --> 00:11:26,101
它的真實價值依舊沒變
The value is still there.

224
00:11:28,104 --> 00:11:31,565
我們剛剛開始談 Min還是很興奮的 但他們還沒有給出具體的數字
We just started. Min's excited, but we haven't heard the terms.

225
00:11:33,151 --> 00:11:34,234
你在哪兒?
Where are you?

226
00:11:34,319 --> 00:11:35,944
我剛走出會議室來接你的電話啊
I just stepped out to take the call.

227
00:11:36,821 --> 00:11:38,489
快回去 要有禮貌啊
Get back in there. Don't be rude.

228
00:11:39,783 --> 00:11:41,575
好的
Okay.

229
00:11:41,659 --> 00:11:44,495
我們只是將你們不感興趣的那一部分資產
We simply take the assets you don't find appealing,

230
00:11:45,538 --> 00:11:47,664
拆分成一個獨立的公司
spin them off into a separate company.

231
00:11:49,959 --> 00:11:52,419
- 你不必買下整家銀行  - 抱歉
- You don't buy that bank.  - I'm very sorry.

232
00:11:52,504 --> 00:11:54,421
你只需買下這家運營良好的銀行就行了
You buy the good bank.

233
00:11:57,217 --> 00:11:58,717
他們對房地產不感興趣
Look, they don't like the real estate.

234
00:11:58,802 --> 00:12:00,135
什麼叫他們不感興趣?
What do you mean, they don't like it?

235
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:03,972
Dick 我們終於有些進展了 暫時不要打擾我了
Dick, we're making real progress here, okay? Let me stay on it for now.

236
00:12:20,031 --> 00:12:22,157
Min 你好
Min, how are you?

237
00:12:22,700 --> 00:12:24,576
很高興見到你
Great to see you.

238
00:12:25,537 --> 00:12:27,121
希望沒有打擾到你們
I don't want to interrupt.

239
00:12:27,414 --> 00:12:29,540
Dick 你來得正是時候
Dick, great timing.

240
00:12:29,624 --> 00:12:32,167
看起來雙方對合同的大致框架都很滿意
We seem to be in sync on the broad strokes of the deal.

241
00:12:32,710 --> 00:12:34,711
我們可以回到意向書上來了嗎?
Shall we get back to the letter of intent?

242
00:12:34,879 --> 00:12:39,675
Min 我不得不告訴你 我覺得你正在犯一個大錯
Min, I have to tell you, I think you're making a big mistake here.

243
00:12:39,843 --> 00:12:42,344
房地產資產價值巨大
There's great value in the real estate assets.

244
00:12:43,555 --> 00:12:45,514
要不通過仔細分析投資組合
How about we walk through the portfolio

245
00:12:46,182 --> 00:12:47,683
我來向你展示這一點如何?
and I'll show you?

246
00:12:50,562 --> 00:12:52,354
我們已經仔細看過了
We have looked at them.

247
00:12:52,439 --> 00:12:56,024
有些地方你肯定沒看懂
Then you must have looked at them in the wrong way.

248
00:12:56,860 --> 00:12:59,653
我不想看你做出錯誤的決定
See, I just don't wanna see you leave money on the table.

249
00:12:59,737 --> 00:13:02,364
或許我們應該休息一下
Perhaps we should take a break.

250
00:13:08,329 --> 00:13:10,456
Min 非常抱歉
Min, I'm so sorry.

251
00:13:10,540 --> 00:13:14,668
我們一直在真心實意地進行談判 突然就這麼回到原點了?
We have negotiated in good faith. Now all of a sudden we are going backward?

252
00:13:14,752 --> 00:13:16,295
我們同意你給出的報價
We can work with you on the price.

253
00:13:16,379 --> 00:13:18,213
這與報價無關
It is not about the price.

254
00:13:18,590 --> 00:13:22,009
我說的是你們處理事情的方式
It is about the way you have conducted this.

255
00:13:27,682 --> 00:13:30,642
非常感謝大家
I'd like to thank you, all of you,

256
00:13:30,935 --> 00:13:34,229
但我覺得已經沒有繼續談下去的基礎了
but I don't think we have a structure that works.

257
00:13:40,445 --> 00:13:41,653
什麼 就這麼結束了?
What, that's it?

258
00:13:41,738 --> 00:13:43,530
你們就打算這麼打道回府了?
You're just gonna pack up and go back to Korea?

259
00:13:57,504 --> 00:13:59,463
- 你好  - Neel 我是Dick Fuld
- Hello?  - Neel, it's Dick Fuld.

260
00:14:01,090 --> 00:14:04,718
聽著 如果Hank想讓我找到買家
Listen, you know, if Hank wants me to find a buyer,

261
00:14:04,802 --> 00:14:06,261
你們得出面幫我一把啊
you guys need to step up and help.

262
00:14:06,638 --> 00:14:08,931
韓國人剛剛退出交易了
The Koreans just walked out, okay?

263
00:14:09,098 --> 00:14:10,641
我只是表達一下自己的觀點
Look, I'm just speaking for myself here,

264
00:14:10,725 --> 00:14:13,060
但我認為你應該做一些有利於公司的事情
but I think you need to do what's right for the firm.

265
00:14:13,144 --> 00:14:14,853
什麼叫有利於?
Do what's right?

266
00:14:14,938 --> 00:14:16,438
這話是什麼意思?
What is that supposed to mean?

267
00:14:16,606 --> 00:14:18,690
如果股價繼續下跌
If your stock price keeps sliding,

268
00:14:18,775 --> 00:14:21,235
你也許會得到一個令人失望的報價
you may get an offer at a price that doesn't look all that compelling,

269
00:14:21,319 --> 00:14:24,279
但為了公司的持續經營 你必須接受它
but you may have to take it just to keep the company intact.

270
00:14:24,697 --> 00:14:26,031
你指什麼樣的買價?
What kind of price are you talking about?

271
00:14:26,282 --> 00:14:27,699
可能會...
Could be...

272
00:14:27,784 --> 00:14:30,077
我指 股價可能在個位數
I mean, it might be low single digits.

273
00:14:32,664 --> 00:14:36,333
二月份 我們公司每股66美元
Last February, we were at 66 a share.

274
00:14:38,336 --> 00:14:42,589
雷曼兄弟可不是貝爾斯登
Lehman Brothers is not Bear Stearns.

275
00:14:42,674 --> 00:14:46,134
我們業績很好的 房地產會復甦的
We've got a great business. Real estate's gonna come back.

276
00:14:46,261 --> 00:14:49,263
我他媽不會把這公司送人的!
I am not fucking giving this company away!

277
00:14:49,764 --> 00:14:51,008
在雷曼兄弟股價因其
While the real estate market has put

278
00:14:51,009 --> 00:14:52,558
房地產業務而備受壓力時
put Lehman Brothers shares under pressure,

279
00:14:52,642 --> 00:14:54,726
房貸巨頭房利美和房地美兩公司傳出報道說
mortgage giants Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac stocks

280
00:14:54,811 --> 00:14:58,105
需要籌資750億美元才能償付其債務 
are suddenly plummeting this morning, after reports the companies

281
00:14:58,189 --> 00:15:02,067
此後 這兩家公司的股價急劇下跌
may need to raise $75 billion just to remain solvent.

282
00:15:02,151 --> 00:15:04,403
因為這兩家公司幾乎擔保了
Because they guarantee such an enormous percentage 

283
00:15:04,487 --> 00:15:05,904
全國大部分的次級貸款
of the nation's mortgages,

284
00:15:05,989 --> 00:15:07,739
有關人士預測政府將會介入
there is renewed speculation that the government

285
00:15:07,824 --> 00:15:09,825
該事態中 收購兩家公司
may have to step in and take them over,

286
00:15:10,243 --> 00:15:13,620
政府介入的可能性也從奧巴馬的競選演講中得到證實
a possibility Barack Obama has now raised on the campaign trail.

287
00:15:13,705 --> 00:15:16,415
若房利美和房地美倒閉了
If Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac collapsed,

288
00:15:16,499 --> 00:15:22,588
那麼將會給整個金融界帶來
then probably the financial system would receive such a body blow

289
00:15:22,672 --> 00:15:25,173
災難性的動盪
that it could be disastrous.

290
00:15:25,508 --> 00:15:29,511
房地美下跌了8% 房利美下跌5%
Freddie just dropped another 8%. Fannie's down 5%.

