Was it a threat?

341
00:18:38,326 --> 00:18:41,953
不 不是 只能算一個友情提示
No, no, it was a friendly reminder

342
00:18:42,038 --> 00:18:44,001
提示我們 只要他們給莫斯科打一個電話
that with a single phone call to Moscow,

343
00:18:44,002 --> 00:18:45,999
我們美國經濟就會全面崩潰
they can take down the entire US economy.

344
00:18:53,883 --> 00:18:58,470
從賬面來看 房利美和房地美簡直就是一團糟
The book says Fannie and Freddie are a nightmare.

