They are in the hole easily tens of billions of dollars.

346
00:19:01,307 --> 00:19:03,558
過不了幾周 他們就無法償還債務了
Another few weeks, they're gonna start defaulting on their debts.

347
00:19:03,643 --> 00:19:04,862
政府得介入干預此事了
We're gonna have to step in. 

348
00:19:04,863 --> 00:19:07,562
我不明白該怎麼做
I don't see how we can avoid it.

349
00:19:10,358 --> 00:19:13,568
看來武器不開一槍是震懾不住市場的
Turns out a bazooka's not that useful unless you fire it.

