It looks very much like we are about to run out of cash.

439
00:23:01,630 --> 00:23:02,797
美國國際集團?
AIG?

440
00:23:02,882 --> 00:23:04,883
我們給您發了一份文件 是一份電子錶格
We've sent over a document. It's a spreadsheet.

441
00:23:04,967 --> 00:23:07,802
當然 這是一份機密文件 但會讓您瞭解我們的困境的
It's confidential, of course, but it might give you some insight.

442
00:23:08,179 --> 00:23:10,472
我正在處理雷曼兄弟的事情 美國銀行要收購他們
I'm in the middle of Lehman. I'm working with B of A.

443
00:23:11,307 --> 00:23:13,475
那您明天能過來一下嗎?
Is there any way you could come over tomorrow?

444
00:23:13,976 --> 00:23:17,395
我會研究下這張表 然後再說吧
I'll take a look at the numbers and we'll talk.

445
00:23:23,069 --> 00:23:25,236
Flowers先生
Mr. Flowers.

446
00:23:28,699 --> 00:23:30,116
誰去開下電視
Somebody put the TV on.

447
00:23:30,451 --> 00:23:32,869
財經頻道在說雷曼兄弟
CNBC's talking about Lehman.

448
00:23:37,583 --> 00:23:40,504
一位熟悉Paulson的...
A person familiar with Paulson's...

449
00:23:40,505 --> 00:23:42,504
一位瞭解財政部長Hank Paulson想法的人透露
Treasury Secretary Hank Paulson's thinking,

450
00:23:42,588 --> 00:23:45,298
在目前這種經濟環境下
and he is saying there will be no government money

451
00:23:45,591 --> 00:23:47,759
政府不會資助美國銀行收購雷曼兄弟
in the resolution of this situation.

452
00:23:47,843 --> 00:23:50,178
他們說雷曼兄弟被收購和貝爾斯登的情況有兩處不同
They're saying two things make the Lehman deal different.

453
00:23:50,262 --> 00:23:52,764
雷曼兄弟收購是市場早已預料到的 並有半年時間
The market's been aware and had time to prepare

454
00:23:52,848 --> 00:23:55,058
可以準備 第二點是...
for over six months. And the second is...

455
00:23:55,142 --> 00:23:57,769
只是電視台在胡扯?
Is that just TV bullshit?

456
00:23:57,853 --> 00:24:00,939
還是Paulson想給我們傳遞的信息?
Or is that Paulson sending us a message?

457
00:24:01,690 --> 00:24:02,774
喂 Chris?
Chris?

458
00:24:10,366 --> 00:24:11,533
什麼? 不好意思
Yeah? Sorry.

459
00:24:15,037 --> 00:24:17,156
"一位財政部部長的朋友"
What exactly does "a person familiar

460
00:24:17,157 --> 00:24:18,456
這到底是什麼意思?
with the Treasury Secretary" mean?

461
00:24:18,666 --> 00:24:20,708
可能有很多的含義
That could mean a lot of things.

462
00:24:21,127 --> 00:24:22,460
是你的某位員工胡言亂語吧?
Did one of your staffers do this?

463
00:24:22,545 --> 00:24:24,546
一定是你十分鐘前解雇了誰吧
Please tell me someone got fired 10 minutes ago.

464
00:24:24,630 --> 00:24:26,464
那是我的意思
The leak came from me.

465
00:24:29,009 --> 00:24:30,387
Hank 你那種公眾宣言
Hank, a public statement like that

466
00:24:30,388 --> 00:24:32,387
可能會引起很多想像不到的災難
can have a lot of unintended consequences.

467
00:24:32,471 --> 00:24:34,148
我們得提醒別的銀行
We had to send a message to the other banks.

468
00:24:34,149 --> 00:24:35,348
讓他們自己解決了
They need to step up.

469
00:24:35,432 --> 00:24:37,392
我的帽子埵A也變不出兔子來了
I don't have another rabbit I can pull out of my hat.

470
00:24:39,311 --> 00:24:42,105
Rodgin Cohen剛打電話給我
Rodgin Cohen just called me.

471
00:24:42,189 --> 00:24:43,441
他說美國銀行的收購團現在
The B of A team is sitting there

472
00:24:43,442 --> 00:24:44,941
坐在那邊在手機上玩打磚塊
playing Brickbreaker on their phones.

473
00:24:45,025 --> 00:24:46,234
他們不想收購了
They don't want this deal.

474
00:24:47,069 --> 00:24:49,008
收購暫停是因為
The deal is hanging by a thread because

475
00:24:49,009 --> 00:24:50,488
他們對雷曼調查得越仔細
the closer they get to Lehman,

476
00:24:50,573 --> 00:24:52,866
就越覺得 這其實是一個廢料排放場
the more it looks like a toxic waste dump.

477
00:24:53,033 --> 00:24:56,452
所以我們得為他們收購做風險上的補償
Which is why at the end of the day we may have to help them,

478
00:24:56,537 --> 00:25:00,039
若您不作出那種公眾宣言的話 這場收購本該是很順利的...
which would be a lot easier if we didn't publicly state that...

479
00:25:00,124 --> 00:25:02,167
我們不能 Tim! 那樣做不合法!
We can't, Tim! Legally, we can't!

480
00:25:02,334 --> 00:25:07,589
若要合法地做 那這場災難我們也沒辦法阻止
Legally, we haven't figured out how yet.

481
00:25:09,091 --> 00:25:12,510
我很擔心
I am concerned

482
00:25:13,262 --> 00:25:18,349
因為我們現在還有幾種挽救措施 但我們正在
we are limiting our options at a time when we have very few,

483
00:25:18,434 --> 00:25:20,101
浪費他們
if any, available.

484
00:25:23,105 --> 00:25:28,735
我想讓那些首席執行官聚集到一起 給他們一個週末的時間
I want all the CEOs in a room. We've got the weekend.

485
00:25:28,819 --> 00:25:30,904
把他們關在美聯儲
We lock them in a room at the Fed

486
00:25:31,155 --> 00:25:34,574
在他們自己解決雷曼兄弟這爛攤子之前 不放他們出來
and we don't let them out until they have a solution on Lehman.

487
00:25:35,117 --> 00:25:36,534
你的燕麥粥快涼了
Your oatmeal's getting cold.

488
00:25:36,619 --> 00:25:39,621
他們會明白事態嚴重性的 他們自己會掏錢的
They'll figure it out. They'll all throw in some money.

489
00:25:41,624 --> 00:25:44,193
Tim強烈建議我們
Tim is advocating strongly that we

490
00:25:44,194 --> 00:25:45,293
央行出面提供一些支援
reconsider some kind of Fed support.

491
00:25:45,544 --> 00:25:47,714
他想讓我們資助所有人
Tim wants us to pick up the tab on everyone.

492
00:25:47,715 --> 00:25:49,714
我可不想做"破產救援大使"
I can't be Mr. Bailout.

493
00:25:50,674 --> 00:25:54,010
而且雷曼兄弟的虧損是貝爾斯登的兩倍
The Lehman hole is twice what Bear's was.

494
00:25:54,094 --> 00:25:55,546
而且投資者正急著從中抽身出來
Investors are pulling their accounts.

495
00:25:55,547 --> 00:25:56,638
你想長期借貸給他們嗎?
You want to lend into a run?

496
00:25:58,641 --> 00:26:00,475
那巴克萊銀行呢? 他們仍想收購雷曼嗎?
What about Barclays? Are they still interested?

497
00:26:00,643 --> 00:26:03,311
他們在對待風險上比美國銀行更加保守
They can't afford the risk any more than B of A can.

498
00:26:04,063 --> 00:26:06,814
我相信你一定能夠說服任何人掏出錢
I don't doubt your ability to talk anybody into submission,

499
00:26:06,899 --> 00:26:09,567
但是這風險確實很大
but it is still a long shot.

500
00:26:09,652 --> 00:26:12,862
而且雷曼兄弟很可能會破產
And there's a very real possibility that Lehman goes under.

501
00:26:12,947 --> 00:26:15,198
這周將會有場收購談判
There's a deal to be made here.

502
00:26:16,992 --> 00:26:18,993
這場談判一定會成功的
I'm gonna make the deal.

503
00:26:19,578 --> 00:26:22,830
在收盤前不到一小時
With just a little more than an hour left until the market 

504
00:26:22,915 --> 00:26:25,416
雷曼兄弟的股價又猛跌了一把
closes, shares of Lehman Brothers have taken another tumble.

505
00:26:25,501 --> 00:26:29,587
股價跌到新低 每股4美元都不到了
The stock is now trading at a new low, under $4 a share.

506
00:26:29,672 --> 00:26:30,988
而且從賣方形勢來看
And judging from the selling,

507
00:26:30,989 --> 00:26:34,300
這種下跌趨勢仍會繼續
there doesn't appear to be a bottom in sight.

508
00:26:37,638 --> 00:26:40,139
除了Blankfein(高盛首席執行官)說他有一場演講 會盡量趕過來的
So, Blankfein has a speech he's trying to get out of,

509
00:26:40,224 --> 00:26:41,266
其他的人都同意了
but the rest have confirmed.

510
00:26:41,350 --> 00:26:43,559
- 告訴他必須來參加  - 好的
- Tell him it's not optional.  - Yeah.

511
00:26:43,811 --> 00:26:46,104
Christopher Cox 美國證交會主席

512
00:26:43,811 --> 00:26:47,104
下午好 主席 歡迎來參加該次會議
Good afternoon, Chairman. Thank you so much for joining us.

513
00:26:46,814 --> 00:26:50,275
- 這架是誰的飛機?  - 呃 這是租來的
- Whose plane is this?  - Uh, that's a rental.

514
00:26:50,359 --> 00:26:51,985
Hank自己掏錢的
Hank put it on his card.

515
00:26:52,069 --> 00:26:55,029
先生 你認識Neel 這是Michele Davis負責公眾事務
Sir, you know Neel and Michele Davis, Public Affairs.

516
00:26:55,114 --> 00:26:56,155
嗨 很高興見面
Hi. Pleasure.

517
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:58,449
- 這位是Dan Jester 我們團隊的新人  - 你好
- This is Dan Jester, our new numbers guy.  - Hi.

518
00:26:58,534 --> 00:27:00,285
是我勸他退休後繼續出來工作的
I talked him into coming out of retirement.

519
00:27:00,369 --> 00:27:02,870
- 什麼? 退休?  - 我們以前在高盛是同事
- Excuse me? Retirement?  - He was with us at Goldman.

520
00:27:03,080 --> 00:27:05,248
財政部還有沒有員工不是從高盛過來的?
Got anybody at Treasury who wasn't at Goldman?

521
00:27:05,332 --> 00:27:06,202
主席 有一點必須澄清一下
Chairman, just to be clear,

522
00:27:06,203 --> 00:27:09,002
我們財政部和高盛之間沒有任何利益衝突
there's no question of conflict of interest.

523
00:27:09,086 --> 00:27:11,796
Hank在任職前就將高盛所有的股份拋售了
Hank sold all of his Goldman stock before he took office.

524
00:27:11,880 --> 00:27:14,215
- 我什麼也沒暗示  - 不好意思
- I wasn't implying anything.  - Sorry.

525
00:27:14,300 --> 00:27:17,385
我們對外面所傳的"高盛政府"的謠言比較敏感
We're a little touchy about the whole "Government Sachs" thing.

526
00:27:18,053 --> 00:27:19,846
我們走吧?
Shall we?

527
00:27:23,434 --> 00:27:25,512
美國銀行發現雷曼的不良資產越來越多
B of A keeps finding more toxic assets.

528
00:27:25,513 --> 00:27:27,812
他們需要政府介入模仿之前摩根大通的收購
They want you to reconsider a Jamie deal.

529
00:27:27,896 --> 00:27:29,482
他們會承擔10億元的損失
They'll split the first billion in losses,

530
00:27:29,483 --> 00:27:31,482
剩餘的40億損失的由政府提供擔保
but they want you on the hook for the next 40.

531
00:27:31,567 --> 00:27:32,859
就像你對貝爾斯登收購做的一樣
You did it for Bear.

532
00:27:34,153 --> 00:27:35,945
Greg 我過會打給你
Greg, let me get back to you.

533
00:27:36,405 --> 00:27:38,691
難道我得在我額頭上紋個字才行嗎?
What, do I have to tattoo it on my forehead?

534
00:27:38,692 --> 00:27:39,991
我們不會對雷曼兄弟收購提供一分錢
We are not bailing out Lehman.

535
00:27:40,075 --> 00:27:41,659
這是華爾街自己賭博失敗
Wall Street has a gambling problem.

536
00:27:41,744 --> 00:27:44,530
若老是讓政府為他們擦屁股
If government keeps covering their losses,

537
00:27:44,531 --> 00:27:45,830
他們永遠也得不到教訓
they never learn anything.

538
00:27:47,708 --> 00:27:49,459
- 怎麼了?  - 我不知道您是想繼續
- What?  - I didn't know if you wanted

539
00:27:49,460 --> 00:27:51,538
教導我道德危機
to keep lecturing me on moral hazard

540
00:27:51,539 --> 00:27:53,838
還是想讓我拒絕美國銀行提議
or if I should just call B of A back.

541
00:27:54,548 --> 00:27:55,559
我們只能讓他們都坐在一起 進行討論
We need to keep them at the table

542
00:27:55,560 --> 00:27:57,759
直到這些企業找到自己的解決方法
until they come up with a private-sector solution.

543
00:27:57,843 --> 00:27:59,427
告訴他們最好照我說的做
Tell them to stay with us.

544
00:28:01,096 --> 00:28:02,889
- Alistair 你好啊  - 你好 Henry
- Alistair, hello.  - Hello, Henry.

545
00:28:02,973 --> 00:28:05,099
請等一下
Hold on one second.

546
00:28:06,602 --> 00:28:08,561
英國財政大臣打來的
Chancellor of the Exchequer.

547
00:28:08,645 --> 00:28:12,023
我瞭解到巴克萊銀行想收購雷曼兄弟
I understand Barclays is one of your potential buyers for Lehman.

548
00:28:12,107 --> 00:28:14,817
但我國的銀行最近的資金壓力也很大
My banks are already under a great deal of stress.

549
00:28:14,902 --> 00:28:16,611
我可不想承擔過多義務
I don't want to become overextended.

550
00:28:16,695 --> 00:28:19,155
雷曼兄弟雖然最近出了問題 但還是有價值的
Lehman is problematic, but there's value there.

551
00:28:19,239 --> 00:28:23,451
我們會讓他能夠盈利的 繼續保持合作吧
We will find a way to make it attractive. Just stay with us.

552
00:28:23,952 --> 00:28:25,119
那再說吧
Talk soon then.

553
00:28:25,204 --> 00:28:26,454
再見
Bye.

554
00:28:26,663 --> 00:28:33,167
2008年9月18日 星期五

555
00:28:26,663 --> 00:28:31,167
我們不會拒絕巴克萊銀行 但最好還是由美國銀行來收購
We'll keep Barclays in the mix, but B of A is still our best bet.

556
00:28:31,668 --> 00:28:35,213
我們今晚會召集所有主要銀行的首席執行官過來開會
We've got the CEOs of every major bank coming here tonight.

557
00:28:35,297 --> 00:28:38,341
我們得明白地告訴他們 這是他們自己捅的簍子
We have to make it clear that this is their problem,

558
00:28:38,425 --> 00:28:41,844
我們政府可以做顧問或是盟友
that we are their advisors and their allies,

559
00:28:41,929 --> 00:28:45,973
但我們不是他們的保險箱
but we are not their safety net.

560
00:28:47,142 --> 00:28:48,476
對這些人 我們還能指望什麼呢?
What should we expect from these guys?

561
00:28:51,842 --> 00:28:54,300
紐約 美聯儲

562
00:28:59,446 --> 00:29:01,239
Jamie很聰明
Jamie is smart.

563
00:29:01,323 --> 00:29:04,450
他買下貝爾斯登後 手頭可運作的資金就不多了
He doesn't have as much cash to work with since he bought Bear.

564
00:29:01,470 --> 00:29:05,450
Jamie Dimon 摩根大通主席兼首席執行官

565
00:29:06,870 --> 00:29:08,746
Lloyd是巨星
Lloyd's a superstar.

566
00:29:09,873 --> 00:29:11,707
高盛是華爾街上最精明的一家
Goldman's the smartest shop on the Block.

567
00:29:11,792 --> 00:29:15,169
雖然我之前當過他老闆 但那並不表示 他就會聽我的了
And just because I used to be his boss, it doesn't mean he's gonna listen to me.

568
00:29:14,180 --> 00:29:16,600
Lloyd Blackfein 高盛主席兼首席執行官

569
00:29:17,256 --> 00:29:20,091
John Mack 他過去常常滿樓層東奔西跑 大呼小叫
John Mack, he used to run around the floor screaming,

570
00:29:20,175 --> 00:29:23,511
"水埵釵撠! 我們殺啊!"
"There's blood in the water! Let's go kill someone!"

571
00:29:24,263 --> 00:29:26,347
他是好戰分子
He's a fighter.

572
00:29:26,370 --> 00:29:28,000
John Mack 摩根士丹利主席兼首席執行官

573
00:29:28,225 --> 00:29:32,019
Thain是我在高盛的副手 他很自私 是個實用主義者
Thain was my number two at Goldman. He's selfish. He's a pragmatist.

574
00:29:32,104 --> 00:29:35,356
他知道 如果雷曼兄弟倒了 下一個就輪到美林證券了
He knows if Lehman goes, Merrill's next.

575
00:29:33,360 --> 00:29:36,300
John Thain 美林證券主席兼首席執行官

576
00:29:37,359 --> 00:29:40,361
Vikram Pandit剛入職花旗
Vikram Pandit is the new guy at Citigroup.

577
00:29:41,947 --> 00:29:45,533
沒人知道 是他在運作花旗 還是花旗在運作他
No one knows if he's running Citi or if Citi's running him.

578
00:29:42,540 --> 00:29:46,000
Vikram Pandit 花旗集團首席執行官

579
00:30:08,724 --> 00:30:11,893
感謝各位匆忙之中趕來這
Thanks for coming down here on such short notice.

580
00:30:12,811 --> 00:30:16,606
下週一早上 雷曼兄弟將無法償付其債務
Monday morning, Lehman will no longer be able to honor its obligations.

581
00:30:19,401 --> 00:30:22,236
有兩家有意購買 美國銀行和巴克萊銀行
We have two potential buyers. B of A and Barclays.

582
00:30:22,321 --> 00:30:26,824
但如果沒有第三方融資 它們都無法完成收購
Neither will take the company unless someone else finances part of the deal.

583
00:30:26,909 --> 00:30:30,203
政府不會進行干預
The government is not in a position to step in.

584
00:30:31,497 --> 00:30:34,582
上一次是最後一次 這次就由你們完成了
I did the last one. You're gonna do this one.

585
00:30:34,708 --> 00:30:36,042
Dick Fuld在哪兒?
Where's Dick Fuld?

586
00:30:36,126 --> 00:30:38,377
Dick不適合再做決定了
Dick's in no condition to make any decisions.

587
00:30:38,462 --> 00:30:41,464
我們將各位分成三組
We're breaking you into three groups.

588
00:30:41,757 --> 00:30:46,385
第一組 評估雷曼兄弟的不良資產
The first one will try to value Lehman's toxic assets.

589
00:30:46,762 --> 00:30:49,972
第二組 設計投資架構 讓大家都可以投資雷曼
The second one will work on some sort of structure for you all to invest in Lehman.

590
00:30:50,390 --> 00:30:54,018
第三組 制定熄燈計劃
And the third one works on the lights-out plan.

591
00:30:54,353 --> 00:30:56,604
如果雷曼兄弟申請破產 我們需要考慮
If Lehman files for bankruptcy, we need to figure out

592
00:30:56,688 --> 00:30:58,898
如何遏制對各家的損害
how to contain the damage to the rest of you.

593
00:30:59,191 --> 00:31:00,274
天吶
Christ.

594
00:31:00,442 --> 00:31:02,151
我們早就預見到會出現這種狀況
We've all seen this coming for miles.

595
00:31:02,236 --> 00:31:05,363
我認為 雷曼兄弟即使破產 也不會給我們公司帶來太大影響
I don't think a Lehman bankruptcy takes down our firms.

596
00:31:05,447 --> 00:31:07,949
所以呢 我們就只能祝福雷曼了嗎?
What, are we crossing our fingers?

597
00:31:08,116 --> 00:31:13,120
這是要求我們挽救競爭對手 別表現得好像在幫我們一樣
You're asking us to save a competitor. Let's not act like you're doing us a favor.

598
00:31:13,664 --> 00:31:17,375
各位 各位 大家都是偉大的美國人
Gentlemen, gentlemen, you are great Americans

599
00:31:17,459 --> 00:31:19,335
這是承擔我們的愛國責任
undertaking a patriotic duty.

600
00:31:19,836 --> 00:31:22,964
各位的努力將為自身贏得
Your travail will earn you the love

601
00:31:23,215 --> 00:31:25,466
舉國的愛戴和感激
and gratitude of your country.

602
00:31:25,717 --> 00:31:27,802
我記得 Thomas Paine(激進民主主義者)曾經說過 "這些..."
I think it was Thomas Paine who said, "These are..."

603
00:31:27,886 --> 00:31:30,096
雷曼兄弟是在座各家銀行的合作夥伴
Lehman is a trading partner for every bank in this room.

604
00:31:30,180 --> 00:31:32,890
它的破產將對大家都有很大衝擊
Their failure will be a massive blow to all of you.

605
00:31:32,975 --> 00:31:34,517
這就是重點
This is your problem.

606
00:31:34,685 --> 00:31:37,562
我們可以好好說說 為何會到如此地步
We can all argue about how we got here.

607
00:31:37,646 --> 00:31:41,232
放鬆管制 衍生品 Dick Fuld決策不利
Deregulation, derivatives, Dick Fuld made bad decisions.

608
00:31:41,608 --> 00:31:44,819
我們都有責任 這是災難性的動盪
We're all responsible. It's a catastrophic mess.

609
00:31:45,737 --> 00:31:48,656
政府已經竭盡所能 現在全靠你們了
The government's done whatever it can do. It's on you now.

610
00:31:49,116 --> 00:31:51,492
各位該解決問題 付出代價了
You need to fix it and you need to pay for it.

611
00:31:51,743 --> 00:31:53,703
我就直說了
Let me be clear.

612
00:31:54,997 --> 00:31:59,500
沒出力的人 我們會記下的
We will remember anyone who is not helpful.

613
00:32:07,997 --> 00:32:16,000
2008年9月13日 星期六

614
00:32:23,275 --> 00:32:25,109
你注意到這其中的小規律了嗎?
Do you notice a little pattern here?

615
00:32:25,193 --> 00:32:27,945
不見棺材不掉淚
We don't deal with things until there's some kind of emergency on the table.

616
00:32:28,030 --> 00:32:30,114
是啊 不到最後一刻 沒人會去處理的
Yeah, we don't deal with things until Friday.

617
00:32:30,198 --> 00:32:31,324
現在一隻腳已經踏進去了
Some kind of a weekend thing.

618
00:32:31,408 --> 00:32:32,450
我們什麼時候才能
When were we gonna figure out

619
00:32:32,534 --> 00:32:34,619
找到解決投資銀行的破產問題的好方法?
exactly how to handle the failure of an investment bank?

620
00:32:34,703 --> 00:32:36,329
週末搞定吧
Let's do it over a weekend.

621
00:32:36,413 --> 00:32:39,790
我剛剛跟一位密切關注現狀的專家談過
I talked to a person who is monitoring the situation out there,

622
00:32:39,875 --> 00:32:44,003
他說 業界人士都期望 他們能和Jamie Dimon一樣 得到政府的自助
and the person said they all want the same deal Jamie Dimon got,

623
00:32:44,087 --> 00:32:46,130
但預計期望會落空
and they're not going to get it.

624
00:32:46,298 --> 00:32:49,383
提醒一句 Chris Flowers正在大廳
Just a heads up, Chris Flowers is in the lobby.

625
00:32:49,468 --> 00:32:52,386
他是美國銀行收購雷曼案的顧問
He's consulting for B of A on Lehman.

626
00:32:53,722 --> 00:32:56,182
Hank之前將Flowers擠出了高盛
Hank pushed Flowers out of Goldman.

627
00:32:56,266 --> 00:32:59,894
昨天我們還認為雷曼的不良資產僅300億 今天就漲到了700億
Yesterday, we thought Lehman was holding 30 billion in crap. Today it's 70.

628
00:33:00,020 --> 00:33:03,397
700億不良資產 這還只是隨機抽樣
$70 billion in assets that we're valuing with a dartboard.

629
00:33:03,482 --> 00:33:04,732
沒事 我們會解決這個問題
No, we're gonna work this out.

630
00:33:05,067 --> 00:33:07,318
除非政府干預 不然我們就停手
Unless you step in, we're ending this.

631
00:33:07,402 --> 00:33:08,694
別忘了Dick
Don't forget about Dick.

632
00:33:08,779 --> 00:33:12,740
好了 Dick Fuld不停打來電話 不停要求我們提高價格
Yeah, Dick Fuld keeps calling, hammering us to raise the price.

633
00:33:14,868 --> 00:33:16,869
抱歉
Excuse me.

634
00:33:20,499 --> 00:33:25,378
700億不良資產 還無擔保?
70 fucking billion and no collateral?

635
00:33:27,422 --> 00:33:29,590
如果雷曼兄弟本週末破產
If Lehman Brothers fails this weekend,

636
00:33:29,675 --> 00:33:33,928
專家們毫不懷疑 下一個將是美林證券
there's little doubt amongst the people I speak to that Merrill Lynch will be next.

637
00:33:34,012 --> 00:33:36,180
信心是非常脆弱的
Confidence is a very fragile thing.

638
00:33:36,264 --> 00:33:39,934
在金融市場 信心的流失速度非常快
And in our financial markets, it is eroding very quickly.

639
00:33:40,018 --> 00:33:45,106
雷曼撐不下去了 我們就是下一個 必須立刻採取措施了
Lehman's not gonna make it. We're next. We need to do something right now.

640
00:33:45,482 --> 00:33:48,776
只有美國銀行能救我們了 我可以打個電話看看
B of A's the only one out there. I can put in a call.

641
00:33:48,860 --> 00:33:50,945
- 雖然這樣會毀了雷曼 不過...  - 雷曼是自食其果
- It screws Lehman, but...  - Lehman screwed themselves.

642
00:33:51,029 --> 00:33:56,534
Paulson已經劃定了底線 雷曼完了 打電話吧
Paulson has drawn a line in the sand. Lehman is dead. Make the call.

643
00:33:59,788 --> 00:34:03,124
你們考慮一下收購美林的股份吧
We'd like you guys to look at taking a stake in Merrill,

644
00:34:03,208 --> 00:34:05,960
有約10%的利潤
something in the neighborhood of 10%.

645
00:34:06,128 --> 00:34:09,797
我不知道能否拿到10%的利潤
I don't know if I can generate any interest in 10%,

646
00:34:10,632 --> 00:34:13,592
不過如果是收購整家公司的話
but if the whole company's in play,

647
00:34:13,677 --> 00:34:15,803
我們肯定是願意考慮一下的
I bet that's something that we'd consider.

648
00:34:15,971 --> 00:34:17,930
我們和雷曼?
Us and Lehman?

649
00:34:18,849 --> 00:34:20,725
這種規模的收購 我們只能完成一家
Deal this size, there's only room for one.

650
00:34:27,566 --> 00:34:32,486
毫無疑問 風險很大 但是只要各位不中途退出
It is a lot of risk, no question, but if you stay in the game,

651
00:34:32,571 --> 00:34:34,989
- 就都能找到各自的解決之道  - 當然了
- we all will find a private solution.  - Absolutely.

652
00:34:37,284 --> 00:34:41,662
別被這些數字嚇到了 我們會解決的 雷曼是值得收購的
Don't get scared by the numbers. We'll figure it out. Lehman is worth owning.

653
00:34:41,747 --> 00:34:44,457
各位 有空嗎?
Guys, you got a second?

654
00:34:48,044 --> 00:34:49,920
我昨天去過了美國國際集團
I was at AIG yesterday.

655
00:34:50,005 --> 00:34:54,592
下週三 他們將有至少50億的缺口
Next Wednesday, they got a $5 billion hole, minimum.

656
00:34:55,761 --> 00:34:59,513
我跟沃倫·巴菲特聯繫過了 他表示絕對不會幫忙
I called Warren Buffett. He wouldn't touch it with a stick.

657
00:35:00,682 --> 00:35:01,932
我們會調查清楚
We're looking into it.

658
00:35:02,017 --> 00:35:03,976
這是一家非常大的公司
It's a very big company.

659
00:35:06,354 --> 00:35:10,357
謝了 Chris 感謝你所有的幫助
Thanks, Chris. I appreciate all your help.

660
00:35:17,532 --> 00:35:19,533
他們根本不瞭解狀況
They're not on top of it.

661
00:35:26,291 --> 00:35:28,375
看看這個
Look at this.

662
00:35:31,922 --> 00:35:34,423
這可能嗎?
Is this even possible?

663
00:35:34,925 --> 00:35:36,258
美國國際集團?
AIG?

664
00:35:36,551 --> 00:35:37,593
該死的
Holy shit.

665
00:35:39,554 --> 00:35:41,138
調查清楚
Get into this.

666
00:35:43,475 --> 00:35:44,517
嘿 John
John.

667
00:35:50,190 --> 00:35:52,775
你明白現在的狀況嗎?
Do you see what's happening here?

668
00:35:53,568 --> 00:35:55,444
你想好怎麼為自己打算了嗎?
Are you watching out for yourself?

669
00:35:55,529 --> 00:35:59,990
我不笨 我正在採取行動
I'm not thick. I'm working on something.

670
00:36:03,620 --> 00:36:05,996
你想去找美國銀行
You're talking to B of A.

671
00:36:07,999 --> 00:36:09,333
抱歉
I'm sorry.

672
00:36:10,377 --> 00:36:12,920
我知道 這樣對雷曼不好 但是我必須先顧好美林
I know it's not good for Lehman, but I have to take care of Merrill.

673
00:36:13,088 --> 00:36:15,464
把雷曼扔給我來操心
Let me worry about Lehman.

674
00:36:16,424 --> 00:36:19,134
巴克萊還沒有退出
Barclays is still in the game.

675
00:36:21,471 --> 00:36:22,596
你去搞定吧
Just get it done.

676
00:36:33,859 --> 00:36:37,361
美國銀行將收購美林
B of A is gonna buy Merrill.

677
00:36:39,906 --> 00:36:41,699
我們必須讓巴克萊出手
We need to make Barclays work.

678
00:36:43,034 --> 00:36:45,327
我記得你說過 英國佬只說不做的
I thought you said the British never close.

679
00:36:46,037 --> 00:36:49,915
他們就在外面 似乎真的很想收購
They're here. They seem to really want it.

680
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:53,210
只要我們主動一點 他們就會收購的
If we hold their hands, they'll close.

681
00:36:53,295 --> 00:36:58,674
Rodgin 怎麼回事? Geithner不接電話 Paulson也不接電話
Rodgin, what the fuck? I can't get Geithner. I can't get Paulson.

682
00:36:58,758 --> 00:37:01,594
連我的手下現在也不接電話了
I can't even get my own goddamn employees to pick up the phone.

683
00:37:01,678 --> 00:37:03,637
Dick 大家都太忙了
There's a lot happening down here, Dick.

684
00:37:03,722 --> 00:37:05,139
噢 該死
Oh, fuck.

685
00:37:05,724 --> 00:37:07,933
給我聽好 你去告訴Geithner
You know what? You tell Geithner,

686
00:37:08,018 --> 00:37:11,061
他要是不幫我把這事解決了 下一個就輪到美林了
he doesn't pull my ass out of the fire, Merrill's gonna be next.

687
00:37:11,187 --> 00:37:12,313
他知道
He knows that.

688
00:37:12,397 --> 00:37:16,775
Dick 他剛告訴我 他們正在為美林尋找出路
Dick, he just told me they're working on a solution for Merrill.

689
00:37:20,196 --> 00:37:22,156
那群混蛋要去幫美林?
Those cocksuckers are gonna bail out Merrill?

690
00:37:22,240 --> 00:37:23,824
不 不是美聯儲
No, no, not the Fed.

691
00:37:24,117 --> 00:37:27,870
沒有私營買家了 只有美國銀行和...
There's no private buyers. There's just B of A and...

692
00:37:29,456 --> 00:37:31,498
他們想讓美國銀行收購美林?
They're gonna put B of A together with Merrill?

693
00:37:31,583 --> 00:37:34,084
還有巴克萊銀行 Hank覺得...
We still have Barclays. Hank feels that...

694
00:37:34,169 --> 00:37:37,963
聯邦政府竟然給我幫倒忙?
The federal government is snaking my deal?

695
00:37:39,299 --> 00:37:41,800
我簡直不敢相信!
I cannot fucking believe this shit!

696
00:37:44,471 --> 00:37:46,221
美國銀行和美林達成協議了?
B of A made a deal with Merrill?

697
00:37:46,306 --> 00:37:48,307
對 雷曼的問題還是沒解決
Yeah, Lehman's still our problem.

698
00:37:47,320 --> 00:37:49,000
2008年9月14日

699
00:37:49,017 --> 00:37:51,143
再來這麼一次 我可受不了了
I don't think I can take another day of this.

700
00:37:51,227 --> 00:37:54,521
你是剛下梅賽德斯 來到紐約美聯儲
You're getting out of a Mercedes to go to the New York Federal Reserve.

701
00:37:54,606 --> 00:37:57,316
可不是奧馬哈海灘的希金斯快艇
It's not a Higgins boat on Omaha Beach.

702
00:38:06,034 --> 00:38:08,786
好了 好了 時間已經夠長了
Okay, okay, we've been here a long time.

703
00:38:09,871 --> 00:38:12,122
別廢話了
Let's stop fucking around.

704
00:38:12,207 --> 00:38:15,125
政府想讓華爾街付賬
Main Street wants Wall Street to pay.

705
00:38:15,210 --> 00:38:18,045
他們覺得 我們就是有錢的笨蛋
They think we're overpaid assholes.

706
00:38:19,047 --> 00:38:21,590
沒有哪條政策規定 一定要參與緊急援助
There's no politician who's gonna sign off on a bailout.

707
00:38:21,675 --> 00:38:25,594
那為什麼不去資助那些賺錢的人呢?
Why would you bail out people whose sole job is to make money?

708
00:38:25,679 --> 00:38:29,598
簡單點說一下現在的狀況吧
So, let's make this real simple.

709
00:38:30,600 --> 00:38:34,478
Hank認為 他可以把雷曼好的資產出售給巴克萊銀行
Hank thinks he can sell the good parts of Lehman to Barclays,

710
00:38:34,562 --> 00:38:38,899
但這樣就得有人把拖垮這家公司的抵押房產接手下來
but someone has to take the real estate crap that's weighing down the company.

711
00:38:38,984 --> 00:38:40,734
誰都不知道這些不良資產的價值
Nobody knows how much this shit is worth,

712
00:38:40,819 --> 00:38:42,945
但我們很清楚 一定得有人買下這批資產 以完成收購
but we know somebody has to buy it to make a deal.

713
00:38:43,405 --> 00:38:47,282
我不喜歡這樣 沒人喜歡這樣
I don't like it. Nobody likes it.

714
00:38:47,826 --> 00:38:50,244
那就別抱怨了 去做吧
Let's just suck it up and do it.

715
00:38:50,620 --> 00:38:56,000
有多少人可以投個10億元 阻止雷曼的頹勢?
How many of you can kick in a billion dollars to stop Lehman from going down?

716
00:38:58,920 --> 00:39:01,505
我投 10億
I'm in. One billion.

717
00:39:14,019 --> 00:39:16,186
好
Okay.

718
00:39:21,484 --> 00:39:24,236
高盛投10億
Goldman's in for a billion.

719
00:39:31,578 --> 00:39:32,995
John 你呢?
John?

720
00:39:34,289 --> 00:39:35,414
喂?
Yeah?

721
00:39:41,421 --> 00:39:42,463
是
Yes.

722
00:39:45,050 --> 00:39:46,133
好
Yeah.

723
00:39:49,262 --> 00:39:50,304
是
Yes.

724
00:39:55,643 --> 00:39:57,895
成功了 巴克萊銀行願意購買
We did it. Barclays came through.

725
00:39:58,146 --> 00:39:59,813
太棒了!
Too goddamn right!

726
00:39:59,898 --> 00:40:04,443
巴克萊不願意要不動產資產 但是其他銀行同意收購這部分了
Barclays won't touch the real estate assets, but the other banks agreed to cover those.

727
00:40:06,488 --> 00:40:10,324
通知董事會 把大家都喊來 我們有交易要談了
Call the board. Get everybody here. We got a deal to make.

728
00:40:10,533 --> 00:40:11,700
好的
Okay.

729
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:21,800
晚上9點 倫敦

730
00:40:21,920 --> 00:40:23,003
找到他了嗎?
Did you get him?

731
00:40:23,088 --> 00:40:25,506
Geithner不回我電話
Geithner doesn't return my calls.

732
00:40:26,341 --> 00:40:27,966
我們一個人都找不到
We can't get hold of any of those people.

733
00:40:28,051 --> 00:40:30,928
今天之前 沒有我們發話 他們是簽不了協議的
At the end of the day, they can't sign the deal without our say-so.

734
00:40:31,012 --> 00:40:33,138
對 但是他們知道嗎?
Yes, but do they know that?

735
00:40:36,768 --> 00:40:37,893
對
Yes.

736
00:40:36,768 --> 00:40:42,893
Callum McCarthy爵士 英國銀監會主席

737
00:40:38,812 --> 00:40:42,689
嗯 一定 既然他屈尊來電 那就放他一馬吧
Yes, by all means, now that he deigns to call, put him through.

738
00:40:43,024 --> 00:40:45,692
Callum爵士 抱歉沒能回電
Sir Callum, sorry I haven't gotten back to you.

739
00:40:45,777 --> 00:40:49,363
我們在處理巴克萊銀行收購雷曼的事宜
We're just sorting through this Barclays deal for Lehman.

740
00:40:50,365 --> 00:40:52,491
身為巴克萊銀行的監管方
As Barclays' regulator,

741
00:40:52,575 --> 00:40:55,494
我們非常關注這樁計劃中的交易
we have serious concerns about this proposed arrangement.

742
00:40:55,578 --> 00:40:59,456
什麼? 你是說你不同意這樁交易?
What? Are you saying you won't approve the deal?

743
00:40:59,541 --> 00:41:03,001
就算我們同意這樁交易 事實上並非如此
Even if we were comfortable with the agreement, which we are not,

744
00:41:03,086 --> 00:41:07,089
巴克萊銀行也需要至少提前30天徵得股東同意
