Hank, it's a complicated situation where...

811
00:45:10,500 --> 00:45:12,417
亞洲要開盤了
Asia's opening.

812
00:45:12,502 --> 00:45:14,252
他們不公告 市場就完了
They don't announce, the market goes in the toilet.

813
00:45:14,337 --> 00:45:17,381
