We have to consider the appropriate role of government here.

814
00:45:17,465 --> 00:45:19,549
我身為證監會主席 能否提議...
Can I, as Chairman of SEC, move forward and...

815
00:45:19,634 --> 00:45:22,052
你們就像是不能出面的幕後人
You guys are like the gang that can't shoot straight.

816
00:45:22,136 --> 00:45:23,804
這就是你們的工作
This is your job.

817
00:45:24,806 --> 00:45:27,974
趕緊去打電話
Make the damn phone call.

818
00:45:35,274 --> 00:45:37,025
Chris 我是Dick Fuld
Chris, this is Dick Fuld.

819
00:45:37,110 --> 00:45:41,780
董事會成員正在開會 大家都到齊了 所有的股東和公司的法律顧問
The board is in session. Everyone is here. All the directors and the firm's counsel.

820
00:45:41,864 --> 00:45:45,242
我們明白和巴克萊的談判已經失敗
We understand the Barclays deal has imploded.

821
00:45:46,702 --> 00:45:52,416
我們在想你們有沒有我們還沒想到的解決方案
We were hoping you might have some option that we haven't thought of yet.

822
00:45:53,042 --> 00:45:56,461
你知道 市場現在處於一團亂的狀態
Um, the markets are in turmoil, as you know.

823
00:45:57,088 --> 00:45:59,214
我相信 雷曼兄弟的破產
A Lehman bankruptcy will help

824
00:45:59,298 --> 00:46:02,050
有助於消除不穩定性因素 起到穩定市場的作用
settle that uncertainty and, we believe, calm the market.

825
